data.description: Landmark property near the Wedge Co-op! Terrific corner up-down duplex with updated garden level unit that has 1BR-3/4 bath, updated and open kitchen to living room and 2 exterior accesses. Unit 2 is a 3-story 4 BR-3BA unit with loads of sun-filled rooms,spacious kitchen, separate dining room, living room and laundry on the main flr, 2 bedroom and full bath on the 2nd flr and 2 bedrooms,3/4 bath and access to the large deck with pergola! Unit 2 has access to the fenced backyard as well! Coveted detached 2-car garage + 2 off-street parking spaces is a plus!  Walk to area shops and restaurants and close to downtown Mpls for work or play!
